text: Azam Khan (born 10 August 1998) is a Pakistani cricketer who plays for Quetta Gladiators and Pakistan Television. He is the son of former Pakistani cricketer Moin Khan. ==Career== He made his List A debut for Pakistan Television in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam One Day Cup on 6 September 2018. He made his Twenty20 debut for the Quetta Gladiators in the 2019 Pakistan Super League on 5 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * * Azam Khan at Pakistan Cricket Board Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Pakistan Television cricketers Category:Quetta Gladiators cricketers
